thread.title: BRIEF-Banca Profilo FY Prelim. Net Profit Up 134 Pct At EUR 5.2 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Banca Profilo FY Prelim. Net Profit Up 134 Pct At EUR 5.2 Mln
text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - BANCA PROFILO SPA:
* REPORTED ON THURSDAY FY PRELIMINARY OPERATING INCOME EUR 59.3 MLN VS EUR 49.9 MLN YEAR AGO
* FY PRELIMINARY NET PROFIT EUR 5.2 MLN VS EUR 2.2 MLN YEAR AGO
* BOARD APPROVES 2018 BUDGET, THUS CONFIRMING 2017-2019 TARGETS
